Oh, Saint Charbel, the amiable, who shines like a bright star in the church sky,brighten my way, and fortify my hope. From you I ask for the grace (mention request here). Ask for it from Jesus the crucified whom you perpetually worship. Amen. Oh, Saint Charbel, the example of patience and silence, intercede for me. Oh, Lord Jesus, who sanctified Saint Charbel and helped him to carry his cross, give me the courage to bear life‚Äôs difficulties with patience and submission to your divine will through Saint Charbel‚Äôs intercession, to you is gratefulness forever. Amen.

Our Father Hail Mary Glory Be

In the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.



