Oh, Saint Charbel, loved by God, enlighten me, help me and teach me how to please God. Hurry to my rescue. Oh affectionate Father; I beg of you to ask God for this grace (mention request here). Oh, Saint Charbel, friend of the crucified, intercede for me. Oh, God hear my request through Saint Charbel‚Äôs intercession. Save my poor heart and give me peace. Calm the troubles of my soul. Glory to you till the end.

Our Father Hail Mary Glory Be

In the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.



