Oh, Saint Charbel, loved by everyone, helper of the needy; I have firm hope in your intercession before God. Fulfill this grace for me (mention request here). Oh, Saint Charbel, a star that counsels the bewildered, intercede for me. Oh, God, my numerous sins hinder your grace to reach me. Grant me the grace to repent. Answer me through Saint Charbel‚Äôs intercession. Return the joy to my sad heart and grant me my request. You, the embodiment of graces, glory and gratefulness be to you.

Our Father Hail Mary Glory Be

In the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.



